_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024882183727313451"}}, "attached_info": "CkkInfSzzoHinaVyEAMaCTExOTA1NDc3OCDd+NLOBjAAOCNAGXITMjAyNDg4MjE4MzcyNzMxMzQ1MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1775625106.994031", "card_id": "Q_2023448343611720005", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《崩坏星穹铁道》中，现在作为无名客的主角和从前作为星核猎手的主角能不能算作同一个人？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "问这问题没别的意思，就是看到现在还有人在玩主角是三岁星核精的梗，即使剧情已明确指出主角曾经是星核猎手。所以我在想会不会是你们觉得现在的无名客主角和从前的星核猎手主角不能算同一个人，至多只是像丹恒和丹枫一样是转世轮回的关系？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6a9dda39d0f36b2ee9565a2f94e4e3ba_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023448343611720005"}}, "attached_info": "CkkInfSzzoHinaVyEAMaCTExOTAxMTEzOSD+ib7OBjAAOA1AGnITMjAyMzQ0ODM0MzYxMTcyMDAwNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1775625106.994407", "card_id": "Q_605841009", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 83}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《一人之下》里，公司为什么一定要毁了炉子，而不是上交保留呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "贝希摩斯在用科学的思路研究将普通人改造成异人，有成果了首先改造应用的群里就是这些雇佣兵，那公司为什么不保留炉子呢？拿他当做一个战略武器一样保留着不用，然后再自己放出点风声和证据，让其他大公司集团都忌惮，如果出现大集团利益冲突的话，公司再使用炉子，对严格筛选考察后的普通人员工升级 (比的就是一个异人生产力)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a7f62c3e395c370b5586769f2ddd67fd_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/qu